---
<section id="comparison" class="py-20 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-display text-[#121417] mb-4">Kenapa Bisnis Anda Butuh Upgrade?</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Masih memakai catatan manual? saatnya beralih ke sistem kasir yang lebih rapi, akurat, dan ramah kantong.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <!-- Bad Option -->
            <div data-aos="fade-right" class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm opacity-80 hover:opacity-100 transition">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6 pb-6 border-b border-slate-100">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-slate-500">Catatan Manual / Buku Kertas</h3>
                </div>
                <ul class="space-y-4">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 14l2-2m0 0l2-2m-2 2l-2-2m2 2l2 2m7-2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                        <span>Buku catatan mudah hilang, sobek, atau terselip.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 14l2-2m0 0l2-2m-2 2l-2-2m2 2l2 2m7-2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                        <span>Pusing saat hitung ulang stok karena sering ada selisih.</span>
                    </li>
                     <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 14l2-2m0 0l2-2m-2 2l-2-2m2 2l2 2m7-2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                        <span>Tidak tahu persis omzet bersih harian secara riil.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 14l2-2m0 0l2-2m-2 2l-2-2m2 2l2 2m7-2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                        <span>Tidak ada histori produk apa yang paling laku minggu ini.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Good Option (Jaripos) -->
            <div data-aos="fade-left" class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border-2 border-[#1f5aa2] shadow-xl relative z-10">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-[#1f5aa2] text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-bl-lg rounded-tr-lg">REKOMENDASI SOLUSI</div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6 pb-6 border-b border-slate-100">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#1f5aa2] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white shadow-md">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-slate-900">Jaripos Smart POS</h3>
                </div>
                <ul class="space-y-4">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-700">
                        <div class="mt-1 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-[#1f5aa2]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#1f5aa2] flex-shrink-0">
                            <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <span class="font-medium">Otomatisasi pencatatan, akses laporan realtime di manapun.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-700">
                        <div class="mt-1 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-[#1f5aa2]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#1f5aa2] flex-shrink-0">
                            <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <span class="font-medium">Stock opname presisi, meminimalisir selisih persediaan barang.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-700">
                        <div class="mt-1 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-[#1f5aa2]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#1f5aa2] flex-shrink-0">
                            <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <span class="font-medium">Sangat terjangkau dengan paket gratis selamanya & trial 14 hari.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-700">
                        <div class="mt-1 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-[#1f5aa2]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#1f5aa2] flex-shrink-0">
                            <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <span class="font-medium">Rekomendasi stok AI bantu belanja barang yang terbukti paling laku.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

